50|$|Luc Guyau (21 June 1948-Thorigny (Vendée)) was Independent Chairperson of the <b>FAO</b> <b>Council</b> (ICC) from 2009 to 2013. He holds {{a degree}} of {{agricultural}} technician. He has been a farmer in his native village from 1970 to 2010, farming with his brother and a nephew a 160 ha dairy farm.|$|E
